data.description: Presenting this exquisite 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom townhouse adorned with fresh paint and brand-new carpeting throughout. Nestled in the highly sought-after Tanyard Springs community in Glen Burnie, this home offers a warm and inviting ambiance.   Upon entry, you'll be welcomed by a gracious foyer that leads to a cozy family room, complete with a convenient half bath. The family room provides access to the garage and a walkout to the covered patio, which can also double as a third bedroom if desired.  Ascend the stairs to the main level, where you'll find a generously sized gourmet eat-in kitchen bathed in natural light. This kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and a gas cooking range, making meal preparation a delight. Additionally, there's an expansive deck for outdoor dining and relaxation, offering ample space for your outdoor furnishings.  Moving to the upper level, you'll encounter the owner's suite and the second bedroom. The owner's suite boasts a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom adorned with ceramic tile, a sliding door shower, and double sinks. Conveniently located in the hallway is a full-sized washer and dryer for your laundry needs. The second bedroom is spacious with abundant closet space and plenty of natural light. The hallway bathroom is a complete full bathroom featuring a generous tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day.  Residents of this community enjoy an array of fantastic amenities, including a community center with an attached fitness center, an outdoor pool, a playground, a dog park, and scenic walking and jogging trails. Easy access to major commuter routes such as I-695, I-97, and MD-Rt.100 simplifies your daily travels, while a plethora of shopping, dining, and entertainment options await you at nearby Arundel Mills and Maryland Live!  Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this wonderful home your own. Act swiftly to make it yours today!
